{"tid":2428751,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"社交移民潮短暫 媒體顧問：企業對MEWE、Clubhouse營銷興趣低","createTime":"2021-03-01T19:00:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T23:06:27.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"17f4a0f5f91b2d944ab203074a6f5f41dbd926da","tid":2428751,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T19:00:17.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎拖累實體經濟，影響廣告市道，有廣告業界表示，他們客戶較往年投放更多資源在網絡營銷。另外，近期出現多個新興社交軟件，例如MeWe、Signal和Clubhouse，有媒體顧問指企業偏向持觀望態度，待「社交移民潮」過後再作決定。<br />\n<br />\n媒體顧問楊永樂（Terry）表示去年疫情令到企業難以經營線下推廣，而且一般消費類產品會投放更多資源在市場營銷，因此經濟不景會影響企業在市場營銷的預算。網絡營銷公司MORE Digital市場總監趙杞芹說，今年客戶較積極活躍，比往年投放更多資源在網絡營銷。她相信即使疫情緩和，但消費習慣已經形成，未來數碼營銷的預算只會有增無減。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210302/QW4ZWLSMUVCWFI5NNT3HLNK4MQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210302%2FQW4ZWLSMUVCWFI5NNT3HLNK4MQ%2F&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt17c9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=dd40d482\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210302%2FQW4ZWLSMUVCWFI5NNT3HLNK4MQ%2F&h=91f77974\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210302/QW4ZWLSMUVCWFI5NNT3HLNK4MQ/</a>"},{"pid":"17074c39b9d85cb32c0ec0f404dcd598ab11bb37","tid":2428751,"uid":9681,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T19:21:55.000Z","msg":"坦白講mewe 唔夠userfriendly"},{"pid":"0a4f1585ef2da751caae683482affb4c21d6f5d0","tid":2428751,"uid":25676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T23:05:43.000Z","msg":"mewe根本就唔好用，轉會只係表態要收Facebook皮"},{"pid":"76a060ab8605c9be681108cf79f62a1f69297d07","tid":2428751,"uid":35820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T23:06:27.000Z","msg":"本身FB都少用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}